2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper focuses on communication technologies and their applications in smart cities, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security): Although not the main focus of the paper, the use of multiple antenna systems may have implications for security and cryptography in smart city applications. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes solutions based on multiple antenna systems, which can be seen as a control system. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper briefly mentions delay-sensitive communication applications, which can be related to multimedia applications in smart cities.
